Class ComponentArraySelectionEditor

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.beans.PropertyEditorSupport
      • com.cafean.client.ui.beans.ComponentArraySelectionEditor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ModelDependent, java.beans.PropertyEditor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    InputVariablesEditor, OutputVariablesEditor
    public class ComponentArraySelectionEditor
extends java.beans.PropertyEditorSupport
implements ModelDependent
    This bean editor contains a label and a button for selecting an array of component references.
